high_descs: Take left turn and walk out of the room, turn left and walk straight and take right turn and take a straight walk towards the remotecontrol.
Take the remotecontrol from the top of the sink.
Hold the remote on the countertop.
Place the remotecontrol below the knife which is on the same countertop.
Move little bit towards the right side of the sink.
Take the remotecontrol from the top of the sink.
Walk towards the left side of the countertop.
Put the remotecontrol on the right side of countertop.
anns.task_desc: Put the RemoteControl on the right side of CounterTop

high_descs: Turn left. Exit the room. After you pass the remotecontrol, turn left. Go straight ahead and when you reach the entrance, turn right. Approach the sink cabinet and turn right.
Grab the remotecontrol above.
Lower the remote control on the countertop.
Place the remote control on top of the countertop on the left.
Turn right, move and then turn left to be in front of the sink.
Grab the remotecontrol.
Turn left. Move over. Turn right to open in front of the countertop.
Place the remote control on the countertop to the left side of the other.
anns.task_desc: Find two RemoteControls and place them on top of a CounterTop.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the remotecontrol.
Take the remotecontrol from the sink tray.
Turn and go near the countertop.
Put the remotecontrol on the countertop.
Turn and go near the sink.
Take another remotecontrol from the sink.
Turn and go near the countertop.
Put the remotecontrol on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Collect the RemoteControl and placed it on the CounterTop.

high_descs: Turn left go pass the remotecontrol, turn right go across to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the remote control on the counter beside the sink.
Turn to the countertop beside the sink.
Place the remote control on the countertop behind the knife.
Turn to the sink.
Pick up the remote control in the sink.
Go back to the left of the countertop beside the sink.
Place the remote control on the countertop to the right of the other remote control.
anns.task_desc: Place two RemoteControl on the CounterTop.
